441
00:20:42,384 --> 00:20:46,054
Quem mexe com as forças do mal
termina como o Cedrico Diggory.

442
00:20:46,138 --> 00:20:47,555
Quem?

443
00:20:47,639 --> 00:20:49,057
-Harry Potter.
